\left(a^{m}\right)^{n}=\left(a^{-\left(-m\right)}\right)^{n}=\left(\left(a^{-1}\right)^{\left(-m\right)}\right)^{n}=\left(a^{-1}\right)^{\left(-m\right)n}=\left(a^{-1}\right)^{\left(-mn\right)}.
